### ── IDENTITY SERVICE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortamı seç: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

### 1. Başarılı login — Admin (mfaPending: true dönmeli)
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin.mueller@automarkt.de",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 2. Başarılı login — Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.bauer@automarkt.de",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 3. Hatalı şifre — 1. deneme (failedLoginCount artar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 4. Hatalı şifre — 2. deneme
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 5. Hatalı şifre — 3. deneme
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 6. Hatalı şifre — 4. deneme
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 7. Hatalı şifre — 5. deneme → hesap kilitlenmeli
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 8. Kilitli hesapla doğru şifre → hâlâ reddedilmeli (LOCKED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer.hoffmann@automarkt.de",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### 9. Profil görüntüle — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/getProfile()
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 10. Profil güncelle — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/updateProfile
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Bauer",
  "phoneNumber": "+49 69 99999999"
}

### 11. Şifre değiştir — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/identity/changePassword
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "Test@1234",
  "newPassword": "Test@1234"
}

### 12. Kullanıcı listesi — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/listUsers()
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 13. Kullanıcı listesi — Customer (reddedilmeli — Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/identity/listUsers()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}